This the descriptionof the AMBA APB project

This project consists of mainly three modules 
	1.APB BRIDGE - the master of the APB 
	2. slave - The slave in the APB system
	3. System - The main module with instantiates all the master and slaves and generates the test vectors of two read and write operation.

In the project TWO slaves have been instantiated and the bus has been shared using tri state buffers between them . These two slaves are nothing but two register files.

APB BRIDGE is the master. It is indicated to start a transfer by asserting the transfer signal and providing the relevant information as read/ writeaddress write value, slave select number.

